      <p></p>
<p>Losing a friend leaves an irreplaceable void.  These messages aim to express understanding and offer a shoulder to lean on during their time of grief. Remember to keep it simple and sincere.</p>
<li>I'm so sorry for your loss. My thoughts are with you.</li>
<li>My heart aches for you.</li>
<li>Sending you lots of love and strength.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and remembering the good times.</li>
<li>May the memories of [Name] bring you comfort.</li>
<li>You are not alone in your grief.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need.</li>
<li>Please accept my deepest condolences.</li>
<li>I'll always cherish our memories together.</li>
<li>Your friend's memory will live on.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace.</li>
<li>May happy memories ease your sorrow.</li>
<li>I'm deeply saddened by your loss.</li>
